Can't wait to give out Axolotls and old pet eggs!! 🥰

Get creative and complete one of the fill-in-the-blank coloring pages, and share your creations with the hashtag #ColorAdoptMe! Make sure to include your Roblox username 🎨

You can download the Coloring pages on our Blog, playadopt.me/blog!

node.text:
Happy update day! Today we're updating the settings! All settings will be reset when you log in, so make sure to change them to your liking! ⚙

This is important for parents who use the Trading settings to protect their child! The update will be released at 8AM PT / 11AM ET / 4PM BST, so in two hours! 😊

#robloxadoptme #adoptmeroblox #roblox #adoptmeupdate️ #adoptmemes
